data.description: Beautifully maintained lake front 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home is move-in ready, in sought after Grand Cay Community. Features open floor plan with great room, formal dining room, and spacious gourmet kitchen with center island, corian countertops, and upgraded cabinets. Owner's suite has beautifully updated bathroom, tray ceilings, and large walk-in closet. Extra flex room is perfect for an office or a 5th bedroom. Dining area is adjacent to the covered, screened-in patio and open lanai, perfect for entertaining. Fenced-in yard, overlooking the lake and fountain, has plenty of room for the addition of a pool. The roof and gutters were replaced in April 2021.  Conveniently located to the beach, shopping, I-95, and St. Johns County ''A'' schools, this standout is ready for you to call home!
